---
const title = "WikiSure™ Demo";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f5f7fa;
        --card: #ffffff;
        --text: #0f172a;
        --muted: #475569;
        --accent: #2563eb;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
          Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 96px 24px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      p.lead {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: var(--muted);
        max-width: 720px;
      }

      .card {
        margin-top: 64px;
        background: var(--card);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 48px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }

      .actions {
        margin-top: 32px;
      }

      button {
        appearance: none;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 14px 24px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 500;
        background: var(--accent);
        color: white;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      button:hover {
        opacity: 0.9;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Why WikiSure™ exists</h1>

      <p class="lead">
        Modern ecosystems fail less because of missing technology —
        and more because of missing shared understanding.
      </p>

      <div class="card">
        <p>
          When platforms, insurers, partners and regulators use the same words
          but mean different things, decisions slow down, responsibility becomes
          unclear, and AI systems amplify the confusion.
        </p>

        <p>
          WikiSure™ introduces a governed semantic layer: definitions are
          explicit, assumptions are visible, and decisions are traceable.
        </p>

        <p>
          AI can assist — but humans remain accountable. Governance is not
          automated away; it is made operable.
        </p>

        <div class="actions">
          <button>Start Demo</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
